    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-安装Hexo"><a href="#1-安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装Hexo"></a>1. 安装Hexo</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install nodejs</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install npm</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-生成博客"><a href="#2-生成博客" class="headerlink" title="2. 生成博客"></a>2. 生成博客</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-配置站点"><a href="#3-配置站点" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置站点"></a>3. 配置站点</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>属性值参照hexo官方文档-<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/。小提示：language为themes/next/languages/目录下的不带扩展名的文件名，如zh-Hans。" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/。小提示：language为themes/next/languages/目录下的不带扩展名的文件名，如zh-Hans。</a></p><h2 id="4-安装Next主题"><a href="#4-安装Next主题" class="headerlink" title="4. 安装Next主题"></a>4. 安装Next主题</h2><ul><li><p>官网下载Next最新版本（<a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next）" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next）</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ wget https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/archive/v5.1.4.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>解压v5.1.4.tar.gz至站点的themes目录下，并将解压后的文件夹名称更改为next</p></li><li><p>更改站点配置文件_config.yml中的theme为next，如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme : next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更改themes/next/_config.yml中的配置，属性值参照next官方文档(<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://theme-next.iissnan.com</a>)</p></li><li><p>更改_config.yml后，可以用yaml-lint校验语法</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/blog <span class="string">'hexo site root directory'</span></span><br><span class="line">$ sudo npm install -g yaml-lint</span><br><span class="line">$ yamllint themes/next/_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置 RSS</p><ul><li><p>安装hexo-generator-feed</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="string">'hexo blog root directory'</span></span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更改next配置文件_config.yml，设定 rss 字段的值</p></li></ul></li><li><p>设置文章版权信息</p><ul><li><p>在目录_config.yml中，设置url：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># URL</span><br><span class="line">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as &apos;http://yoursite.com/child&apos; and root as &apos;/child/&apos;</span><br><span class="line">url: http://samuelbaizg.github.io</span><br><span class="line">root: /</span><br><span class="line">permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/</span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在目录themes/_config.yml，打开文章版权设置和license：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post_copyright:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  license: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</span><br><span class="line">  license_url: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>发文章时增加版权信息copyright: true，如下：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Fedora-基于Hexo搭建博客</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-02-24 20:28:58</span><br><span class="line">categories: [其它]</span><br><span class="line">tags: [Hexo]</span><br><span class="line">copyright : true</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改版权内容和样式<br>修改themes/next/layout/_macro/post-copyright.swig和themes/next/source/css/_common/components/post/post-copyright.styl文件即可</p></li><li>Ctrl+C或者鼠标右键点击复制时，拷贝内容增加版权信息<br>待补充</li></ul></li><li><p>修改主题宽度<br>主题变量定义/themes/next/source/css/_variables/主题名.styl，如/themes/next/source/css/_variables/Gemini.styl，如下：</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// --------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">$body-bg-color                    = #eee</span><br><span class="line">$main-desktop                     = 100%</span><br><span class="line">$sidebar-desktop                  = 240px</span><br><span class="line">$content-desktop                  = calc(100% - 252px)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中的$main-desktop为主题桌面跨度，可根据自己喜好设置，如75%，85%，100%等任意值。</p><h2 id="4-部署到Github"><a href="#4-部署到Github" class="headerlink" title="4. 部署到Github"></a>4. 部署到Github</h2><ul><li>在github上注册账号，比如：samuelbaizg</li><li><p>在_config.yml, 配置github部署信息，比如：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/samuelbaizg/samuelbaizg.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>运行如下命令部署到Github</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
