    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-安装Visual-Studio-Code"><a href="#1-安装Visual-Studio-Code" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装Visual Studio Code"></a>1. 安装Visual Studio Code</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo rpm --import https://packages.microsoft.com/keys/microsoft.asc</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo sh -c <span class="string">'echo -e "[code]\nname=Visual Studio Code\nbaseurl=https://packages.microsoft.com/yumrepos/vscode\nenabled=1\ngpgcheck=1\ngpgkey=https://packages.microsoft.com/keys/microsoft.asc" &gt; /etc/yum.repos.d/vscode.repo'</span> </span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf check-update</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install code</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-安装配置RPMFusion"><a href="#2-安装配置RPMFusion" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装配置RPMFusion"></a>2. 安装配置RPMFusion</h2><ul><li><p>安装RPMFusion安装包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck http://download1.rpmfusion.org/free/fedora/rpmfusion-free-release-$(rpm -E %fedora).noarch.rpm http://download1.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/fedora/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-$(rpm -E %fedora).noarch.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改RPMFusion源指向清华TUNA镜像<br>修改 /etc/yum.repos.d/ 目录下以 rpmfusion 开头、以 .repo 结尾的文件, 将其中的baseurl=开头的行等号后面链接中的 <a href="http://download1.rpmfusion.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://download1.rpmfusion.org/</a> 替换为<a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/rpmfusion/，其他属性值保持不变，修改后的baseurl和metalink样例如下：" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/rpmfusion/，其他属性值保持不变，修改后的baseurl和metalink样例如下：</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[rpmfusion-free]</span><br><span class="line">baseurl=https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/rpmfusion/free/fedora/releases/$releasever/Everything/$basearch/os/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="3-升级Fedora软件"><a href="#3-升级Fedora软件" class="headerlink" title="3. 升级Fedora软件"></a>3. 升级Fedora软件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf upgrade --refresh</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf isntall vim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-gedit支持中文"><a href="#4-gedit支持中文" class="headerlink" title="4. gedit支持中文"></a>4. gedit支持中文</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ gsettings <span class="built_in">set</span> org.gnome.gedit.preferences.encodings candidate-encodings <span class="string">"['GB18030','GB2312','GBK', 'UTF-8', 'CURRENT', 'ISO-8859-15', 'UTF-16']"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-安装libeoffice中文语言包"><a href="#5-安装libeoffice中文语言包" class="headerlink" title="5. 安装libeoffice中文语言包"></a>5. 安装libeoffice中文语言包</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install libreoffice-langpack-zh-Han*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="6-安装p7z等压缩插件"><a href="#6-安装p7z等压缩插件" class="headerlink" title="6. 安装p7z等压缩插件"></a>6. 安装p7z等压缩插件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install p7zip p7zip-plugins unrar unzip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="7-安装gnome-tewaks"><a href="#7-安装gnome-tewaks" class="headerlink" title="7. 安装gnome-tewaks"></a>7. 安装gnome-tewaks</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install gnome-tweaks</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="8-安装Chrome"><a href="#8-安装Chrome" class="headerlink" title="8. 安装Chrome"></a>8. 安装Chrome</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install fedora-workstation-repositories</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf config-manager --<span class="built_in">set</span>-enabled google-chrome</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install google-chrome-stable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="9-安装Python3和Pycharm"><a href="#9-安装Python3和Pycharm" class="headerlink" title="9. 安装Python3和Pycharm"></a>9. 安装Python3和Pycharm</h2><ul><li><p>安装依赖库</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install gcc openssl-devel bzip2-devel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装Python（Fedora29默认安装了Python3.7.2）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/Downloads/</span><br><span class="line">$ wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.6.7/Python-3.6.7.tgz</span><br><span class="line">$ tar xzf Python-3.6.7.tgz</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> Python-3.6.7</span><br><span class="line">$ ./configure --<span class="built_in">enable</span>-optimizations</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo make altinstall</span><br><span class="line">$ rm -rf Python-3.6.7</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo pip3.6 install virtualenv</span><br><span class="line">$ python3.6 --version</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo pip3.6 install virtualenv</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo pip3.6 install --upgrade pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>备注：make altinstall避免替换默认的/usr/bin/python。</p><ul><li><p>安装Pycharm<br>官网下载Pycharm Fedora安装包，解压到某一个目录下即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/Downloads/</span><br><span class="line">$ wget https://download.jetbrains.com/python/pycharm-community-2018.3.4.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">$ tar xzvf pycharm-community-2018.3.4.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo mv pycharm-community-2018.3.4 /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span></span><br><span class="line">$ sudo ln -s /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/pycharm-community-2018.3.4/ pycharm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>建立Pycharm桌面快捷链接</p><ul><li><p>在/usr/share/applications目录下建立Pycharm.desktop文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /usr/share/applications/Pycharm.desktop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>拷贝如下内容到Pycharm.desktop中，并保存。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Desktop Entry]</span><br><span class="line">Type=Application</span><br><span class="line">Name=Pycharm</span><br><span class="line">GenericName=Pycharm3</span><br><span class="line">Comment=Pycharm3:The Python IDE</span><br><span class="line">Exec=sh /usr/local/pycharm/bin/pycharm.sh</span><br><span class="line">Icon=/usr/local/pycharm/bin/pycharm.png</span><br><span class="line">Terminal=pycharm</span><br><span class="line">Categories=Pycharm;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><p>备注：上述内容需要将Exec和Icon改成文件实际的路径</p><ul><li>在应用程序菜单里可以找到Pycharm，点击打开Pycharm程序,也可以右键将Pycharm添加到Favorite菜单中</li></ul><h2 id="10-安装MySQL"><a href="#10-安装MySQL" class="headerlink" title="10. 安装MySQL"></a>10. 安装MySQL</h2><ul><li><p>安装MySQL Server</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install libaio</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/Downloads/</span><br><span class="line">$ wget https://cdn.mysql.com//Downloads/MySQL-5.7/mysql-5.7.25-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">$ tar xzvf mysql-5.7.25-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo mv mysql-5.7.25-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64 /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span></span><br><span class="line">$ sudo ln -s /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/mysql-5.7.24-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64/ mysql</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo service sssd stop</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo groupadd mysql</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo useradd -r -g mysql -s /bin/<span class="literal">false</span> mysql</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> mysql</span><br><span class="line">$ mkdir mysql-files</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo chown mysql:mysql mysql-files</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo chmod 750 mysql-files</span><br><span class="line">$ bin/mysqld --initialize --user=mysql</span><br><span class="line">记住行末尾的root的临时密码</span><br><span class="line">$ bin/mysql_ssl_rsa_setup</span><br><span class="line">$ bin/mysqld_safe --user=mysql &amp;</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo cp support-files/mysql.server /etc/init.d/mysql.server</span><br><span class="line">$ bin/mysql -uroot -p</span><br><span class="line">输入root的临时秘密</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; alter user <span class="string">'root'</span>@<span class="string">'localhost'</span> identified by <span class="string">'123456'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; use mysql;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; update user <span class="built_in">set</span> user.Host=<span class="string">'%'</span> <span class="built_in">where</span> user.User=<span class="string">'root'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; flush privileges;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; quit;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装MySQL Workbench</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/Downloads/</span><br><span class="line">$ wget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/MySQLGUITools/mysql-workbench-community-8.0.15-1.fc29.x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo dnf install mysql-workbench-community-8.0.15-1.fc29.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
